the objective of the POC ( 3 days )

1. a microfront end application having 3 pages 
--> a login page 
--> a home page ( a protected page) 
--> a my account page ( a protected page )
--> a registration page ( a non protected page )
--> an error page 

2. a BFF layer using graphql and rest based APIs 

--> a protected API 
--> a non protected API 
--> a shielded API 


Step 1 
we will be using keycloak for the login 

Step 2 
we will be using Microsoft AD as well 

Step 3 
we will try to validate the SSO in jboss 

Landing page urls 

--> /login 
--> /home
--> /my-account
--> /register 

